patthana8.29:4.1: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:4.2: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca dhammaṃ paṭicca naaganthaniyo ceva nano ca gantho dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:4.3: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca naaganthaniyo ceva nano ca gantho ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. #3
patthana8.29:5.1: Naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naaganthaniyo ceva nanogantho ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:5.2: Naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana8.29:5.3: Naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca naaganthaniyo ceva nano ca gantho ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. #3
patthana8.29:6.1: Naganthañceva naaganthaniyañca naaganthaniyañceva nano ca ganthañca dhammaṃ paṭicca nagantho ceva naaganthaniyo ca dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.29:7.1: Hetuyā nava … pe … vipāke ekaṃ … pe … avigate nava.
